{"tid":1984832,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"立會投唔投票就好比食唔食低質黃店","createTime":"2020-04-22T17:23:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T01:23:35.000Z","uid":81657,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8a627d6bb70b8dd44d2bf53d95e708d0bf8c8323","tid":1984832,"uid":81657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T17:23:40.000Z","msg":"好食嘅黃店 = 本土派 （喺呢個港共議會無存在過）<br />\n難食嘅黃店 = 泛民 （不包括賣主黨）<br />\n綠店 = 賣主黨 / 中間游離派<br />\n藍店 = 民賤聯 / 工賊會<br />\n<br />\n就算難食都要食嘅食客 = 現今嘅黃c<br />\n因為得難食黃店而唔想食嘅人 = 白票班人<br />\n食評家 = 現今網上藍黃KOL<br />\n<br />\n冀望米國空投糧食 = 佛系諗法，因為米國啲野食一定唔會食死你，但你呢刻都唔會知質素會係點<br />\n<br />\n但重點！問題係而家你好撚肚餓，你會點揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啱啱煮宵夜時諗，大家點睇呢個比喻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"450259d1d1e1eee9a32c5e2f3e68c3a2d014a189","tid":1984832,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T17:25:47.000Z","msg":"咁我投白票算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927cc12c0a542285bb6e15257fa91fd0bdc68dfa","tid":1984832,"uid":81657,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"450259d1d1e1eee9a32c5e2f3e68c3a2d014a189","tid":1984832,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T17:25:47.000Z","msg":"咁我投白票算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T17:30:31.000Z","msg":"但係你都係無行動，諗唔到方法解決你肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8389fe0413e79ad31792cca56db40b678ce8da96","tid":1984832,"uid":81657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T17:42:24.000Z","msg":"求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"163a7eb42e49eb099b73e4d5402b5710210c12a4","tid":1984832,"uid":2200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8389fe0413e79ad31792cca56db40b678ce8da96","